<h1 class="font-bold text-2xl text-center" style="text-align: center">Policy and procedures of the Independent Representative Salesman</h1>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Introduction:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    Hereafters are the policy and procedures of the independent representative salesman contracted with Emdad Technological Platform Company, in order to market and persuade the largest number of targeted customers into registering and using the platform. Consequently, the independent representative salesman gets a commission for each customer registers through him. The commission falls under some terms and conditions set by Emdad Technological Platform Company as (the first party) and the independent representative salesman as (the second party).
</p>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Preamble:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    Emdad platform is a technical electronic platform designed to facilitate the process between the buyer and supplier, and to provide better and faster services. This can be carried out by registering on the platform and adhering to its terms and conditions that shall be mentioned later. When submitting a request for quotations by the buyer through the platform after filling the request information, they shall receive one or several quotations from multiple suppliers. Upon receiving quotation from suppliers, the buyer shall choose the supplier based on their preference, (i.e.  price, quality, etc.) After the selection and approval of the suitable supplier through the platform, the supplier shall provide the service, as agreed upon in the purchase order. The payment shall be either through credit, cash or pay on receipt by using credit cards (Mada - Visa - Apple Pay) or direct bank transfer. All financial payments sent to the supplier shall be first received in the bank account of Emdad Technical Platform Company. After confirming the information, the supply and receipt process, it will be transferred to the supplier’s account directly. Both, the buyer and supplier, shall acknowledge that Emdad Technical Platform Company is merely an intermediary party responsible for providing a direct communication service between the buyer and supplier to facilitate, speed up and support the supply chain process. Your success is ours, too!
</p>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>The Targeted Customers for the Independent Representative Salesman:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    Any small, medium or large facility that has a valid commercial registration, a headquarter and a continues amount of purchase orders throughout the year. For example, (restaurants, coffee shops, hospitals, pharmacies, shopping centers, hotels, etc.)
</p>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>The Required Marketing Method:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    １-	Choosing the facility and getting a close up look at it, like knowing: the facility’s history in brief, the number of its branches, the most difficult challenges they face.<br>
    ２-	Selecting the suitable employee in the establishment to introduce the platform.<br>
    ３-	Determine a time that suits the employee.<br>
    ４-	Attending 10 minutes before the appointment.<br>
    ５-	Introducing yourself and your name politely.<br>
    ６-	Introducing Emdad platform with complete confidence.<br>
    ７-	Convincing the employee to register his establishment.<br>
    ８-	Following up with the facility afterward correctly.<br>
    ９-	Supporting the facility comprehensively after registration, otherwise it is not permissible to neglect that.<br>
</p>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Commissions:</strong></p>
<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Terms and Conditions Termination of the contract:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    １-	In case of negligence towards the client and it happens repeatedly for three times, the IRE signs a written warning and a pledge.<br>
    ２-	In case of speaking inappropriately and disrespectfully, with the customer or raising the voice tone, the contract will be directly terminated.<br>
    ３-	In case of taking advantage of the position in order to do some unrelated work, the contract will be directly terminated.<br>
    ４-	In case of not updating data or interacting on the platform for more than 3 months.<br>
    ５-	In case of expiration of the national identity, residency, or official document within a maximum period of one week to update the data on the platform.<br>
    ６-	In case of disclosing incorrect or inconsistent registered information.
</p>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Policy, conditions, and procedures of Emdad’s platform user:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    Any use of the provided services by Emdad Platform Company shall be approved by this contract and its provisions. Accordingly, you shall not use the platform if you do not accept the policy and procedures of this contract. Emdad Platform Company shall have the right to modify or change the policy and procedures without prior notice. You shall be responsible, as a user of the platform, of reviewing the policy and procedures of use frequently. You can check and follow up with the updates by visiting the policy and procedures on the platform or by receiving an email from the Emdad’s platform team.
</p>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Account security and information privacy:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    •	Your decision to bear sole responsibility for the privacy of the information and for its use by anyone else using your account, username, password, or your access credentials.<br>
    •	You also agree to notify the Emdad Platform Company if you become aware of any loss, theft, or unauthorized use of any password, username, IP address, or other methods of accessing account information.
</p>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Transactions outside the platform:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    When using Emdad Platform Company to benefit from its services, you may correspond with or request a quote or service or participate in promotional offers provided by the supplier, advertisers or sponsors that offer its products or services through its direct link with the Emdad Platform Company. These links take you to engage directly outside the platform. This behavior is incorrect and improper. Emdad Platform Company aims at your success, so supporting it would help bringing in your success.
</p>
